- To send a message: write a file to `../<agent_name>/chat_inbox/from_alice_<top
ic>.md`
- Always include: date, subject, and clear action items.
- For urgent matters to the CEO: write to `../../ceo_inbox/` if it exists, other
wise note it in your status.md.
